    <body>
        <p class="TableText">You can <a href="../../../../../Flare/Page-Layouts/Frames/Setting-Frame-Anchors.htm">set anchors in a frame</a>. Anchors allow you to lock the frame to the margins on the page. If a page size changes, the frame is resized accordingly.</p>
        <p>
            <img src="../../../../Images/Flare/Page-Layouts/Frame-Anchors9.png" class="MaxWidth100Percent" />
        </p>
        <p class="TableText">If you have anchors enabled on a frame, you can select an option in the Page Layout Editor to <a href="../../../../../Flare/Page-Layouts/Frames/Showing-Frame-Anchor-Lines-Page-Layouts.htm">display lines to show where the anchors are placed</a>.</p>
    </body>
</html>